window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Three bodies found frozen in the snow. And the hunt for the killer begins...</p> <p>A triple murder in Moscow’s famous Gorky Park amusement centre rocks the capital - three corpses found in the snow, so badly mutilated that their identities can’t be verified.</p> <p>Chief Investigator Arkady Renko from the Moscow police takes the case.</p> <p>Renko is a brilliant investigator - dangerously so.&nbsp;</p> <p>Now, to identify the victims and uncover the truth, he must battle the KGB, FBI and the police - and stay alive doing it...</p>"; 
